job
Class Range

java.lang.Object
  job.Range

public class Range
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains queries that have been joined together, so that fewer requests will be sent to the web server. Each ChromosomeQuery Object is distinguished by chromosome number/letter as well as location on the chromosome. Queries that are within a certain distance of each other on a chromosome may be joined together into a ChromosomeQuery. A ChromosomeQuery object shares the same sequence.
